briefTitle: Fujifilm DBT Plus S-View Versus FFDM Alone in the Detection of Breast Cancer - A Pivotal Study
officialTitle: A Multi-Reader Multi-Case Controlled Clinical Trial to Evaluate the Comparative Accuracy of the Fujifilm DBT Plus S-View Versus FFDM Alone in the Detection of Breast Cancer - A Pivotal Study
primaryOutcomeMeasure: Compare Per Subject AUC: DBT Plus S-View Versus FFDM
eligibilityCriteria:
Inclusion Criteria:

* •Female subjects participating in FMSU2013-004A protocol with known clinical status
